1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 6=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Pan Yang Struck Down by a Meteorite)

4
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,470
Your Highness, spare me!

5
00:00:54,470 --> 00:00:55,560
I didn't mean it!

6
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,640
Please spare me!

7
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,670
Enough talk.

8
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,110
Stand still.

9
00:01:00,370 --> 00:01:00,960
Your Highness.

10
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:01,710
You be quiet too.

11
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,280
Your Highness, spare me!

12
00:01:18,310 --> 00:01:20,040
You injured my arm.

13
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,280
Someone else.

14
00:01:27,710 --> 00:01:28,920
You... You.

15
00:01:30,510 --> 00:01:31,230
Me?

16
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:32,400
Come here.

17
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,350
Pick up a rock.

18
00:01:41,150 --> 00:01:41,860
Throw it at him.

19
00:01:44,870 --> 00:01:47,000
I... I don't know how.

20
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,350
How am I supposed to throw it?

21
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,350
Yang.

22
00:01:58,710 --> 00:02:00,680
My aim is terrible.

23
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:02,350
Are you alright?

24
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,280
(Oh no.)

25
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,040
(An enemy couldn't have done worse.)

26
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:10,080
(No wonder Jiang Shuo
keeps telling me not to get married.)

27
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,240
Keep throwing.

28
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:13,280
He's fine.

29
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:14,710
Yes.

30
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:37,870
My lady, open your eyes.

31
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,520
Yang!

32
00:02:58,260 --> 00:03:00,430
Which of you is in charge
of the Li family's business?

33
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:04,120
(So His Highness came to
the Pan Residence looking for me.)

34
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,120
Your Highness,

35
00:03:06,150 --> 00:03:07,310
that would be me.

36
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:10,840
Not Li Qingqing.

37
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:15,750
I... I usually stay out
of public affairs.

38
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:18,520
Qingqing handles them on my behalf.

39
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,670
(Trying to steal the credit?)

40
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,560
(That fool Yuanzhao.)

41
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,620
(This works out perfectly.)

42
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:25,240
(The one in charge of Li Qingqing.)

43
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:27,800
(Her age and appearance both fit.)

44
00:03:28,060 --> 00:03:29,910
(There's a very good chance
she's the Tower Master.)

45
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:31,840
The rest of you may leave.

46
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:34,310
I have something
to discuss with Miss Li in private.

47
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,630
- Yes.
- Yes.

48
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:47,020
(Fortune, Prosperity, and Harmony)

49
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:48,240
Yang! How are you?

50
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,630
Yang, are you alright?

51
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:52,560
Where are you hurt?

52
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,310
Are you alright?

53
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,310
For your sake,

54
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,840
my punishment of General Pan

55
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,310
wasn't too severe, was it?

56
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,430
Yang simply failed
to recognize Your Highness

57
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,750
and offended you by mistake.

58
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:09,470
What happened today
was by no means intentional.

59
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:12,750
I was even planning to recommend Yang
to serve under Your Highness.

60
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,380
We can discuss that another time.

61
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,390
Please give me the strategy
for making money first.

62
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,560
Otherwise, I won't be able

63
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,790
to prepare for your grand plan.

64
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:22,360
What strategy?

65
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,070
We're old friends.

66
00:04:25,330 --> 00:04:26,920
There's no need to keep
your guard up around me.

67
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:29,560
Don't worry.

68
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,870
I won't tell anyone your secret.

69
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:36,870
I don't know how I
may have offended Your Highness.

70
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,680
I beg Your Highness to forgive me.

71
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,120
(Could it really not be her?)

72
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,870
(With the Tower Master's temper,)

73
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:45,630
(I'd be lucky
if she didn't slap me twice.)

74
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,040
Turn around. Let me have a look.

75
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,390
Didn't you hear

76
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:54,270
what I said?

77
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:06,190
Stop.

78
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:08,000
Hold out your hand.

79
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,870
(No trace of nail polish.)

80
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,270
(She's not the Tower Master.)

81
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,310
Answer me.

82
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:36,040
Who's really in charge
of the Li family's business?

83
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,430
Tell me the truth.

84
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,000
Yes.

85
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,190
Li Qingqing.

86
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,430
Just as I thought.

87
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:51,870
Where's Miss Qingqing?

88
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,510
Your Highness,

89
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,500
Qingqing has returned to her room.

90
00:05:58,130 --> 00:06:00,710
(The Tower Master clearly doesn't want
anyone to know who she really is.)

91
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,990
(If I go looking for her now,
I'll definitely get slapped.)

92
00:06:04,660 --> 00:06:06,360
From now on,
all of you behave yourselves.

93
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,310
Understood?

94
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,830
- Yes.
- Yes.

95
00:06:13,190 --> 00:06:14,070
My son.

96
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,720
Yang!

97
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,120
My son.

98
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,310
Are you alright?

99
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:19,430
My son.

100
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,870
Rice balls!

101
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,950
Soft and delicious!

102
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,990
The Supreme Rice Ball
that's bursting with flavor!

103
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,040
Sweet, sour, bitter,
spicy, salty, and savory.

104
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:30,360
We've got every flavor!

105
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,830
Generous fillings!

106
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,870
Come and try one!

107
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,950
He scared me!

108
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,000
What are you doing?

109
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,510
What's all this?

110
00:06:38,510 --> 00:06:39,000
Who's there?

111
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:42,830
What are you selling?

112
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:44,160
Hey,

113
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,000
what is this?

114
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,040
Give me one.

115
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,510
What flavor would you like?

116
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,830
I've never seen
anything like this before.

117
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:51,830
Just pick for me.

118
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,120
It's only a rice ball.

119
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,270
How expensive can it be?

120
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,310
Liu.

121
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:03,040
Wang.

122
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,720
Thanks for recommending that doctor.

123
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,160
Don't mention it.

124
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,360
Twenty wen.

125
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,310
Are you robbing me?

126
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,190
It's just a rice ball.

127
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:14,390
You're charging twenty wen?

128
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:16,120
You were the one who told me to choose.

129
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,920
What?

130
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,120
Trying to eat without paying?

131
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:20,160
No.

132
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:21,920
Twenty wen, right?

133
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:28,160
Take a bite.

134
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:29,950
I...

135
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:32,000
I'll take it home and eat it later.

136
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,070
Eat it now.

137
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:37,360
Then tell me honestly what you think.

138
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:38,870
Tell you?

139
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:39,600
Well...

140
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,270
Sir,

141
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:42,800
were you an official before?

142
00:07:42,870 --> 00:07:43,750
Cut the nonsense.

143
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:44,870
Eat.

144
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:46,950
Okay.

145
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,920
Interesting.

146
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,000
What's wrong with you?

147
00:07:55,010 --> 00:07:56,900
I told you to tell me what you think.
Why are you just grunting?

148
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,120
I haven't had much schooling.

149
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,680
I can't really put it into words.

150
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,040
But I know it's delicious.

151
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,720
This rice ball is worth twenty wen.

152
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:05,270
How about this?

153
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,630
Could I have another one?

154
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:08,310
I'll take it home for my wife.

155
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,070
Excellent.

156
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:15,120
As long as it tastes good,

157
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,920
it'll sell even if it's pricey.

158
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:19,680
My plan will work.

159
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,040
Thank you.

160
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:25,120
By order of the Crown Prince,
search all suspicious persons.

161
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:26,510
Everyone is to be inspected.

162
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:30,950
Officer!

163
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:31,480
Everyone, come over here!

164
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,390
I'd like to report someone.

165
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,240
He's suspicious.

166
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:40,120
What's this?

167
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:40,670
And you?

168
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:42,480
I just stepped out.

169
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,480
Come here.

170
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,200
What about you?

171
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:50,440
After him!

172
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,120
- Yes!
- Yes!

173
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,120
(Qingqing.)

174
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,320
(You really won't leave me any way out.)

175
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,360
(Zheng Yuanhe, just you wait.)

176
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:26,960
Li Qingqing!

177
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,670
Heavens, if I've done something wrong,

178
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:32,960
send the police to punish me.

179
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:35,080
Why send these two idiots
to torture my eyes?

180
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,910
What are you up to now?

181
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:41,720
You shameless woman.

182
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:44,550
Didn't you keep demanding a divorce?

183
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,440
Pack your things.

184
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:47,720
Take the divorce papers.

185
00:09:48,070 --> 00:09:49,240
Get out of the Pan Residence.

186
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,960
I built this house.

187
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:53,390
If anyone's leaving,
it's the two of you.

188
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:56,720
You shameless jerk.
How dare you divorce me?

189
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,960
Just wait.

190
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,990
I'm going back to write
the divorce papers right now.

191
00:10:01,550 --> 00:10:02,320
Stop right there!

192
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,270
You want a divorce?

193
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,720
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

194
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,270
(Why did he follow me here?)

195
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:12,120
(Jiuzhu is so unreliable.)

196
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,240
(I'm done for.)

197
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:15,030
Your Highness,

198
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:16,150
what brings you here?

199
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:17,870
So I can make
the necessary preparations.

200
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,510
You...

201
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:21,670
want a divorce?

202
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:23,750
(What's he up to?)

203
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,030
(Could he still be thinking about)

204
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:26,670
(the incident where Wangshi Tower
surrounded Pan Yang?)

205
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:27,600
(and trying to test me?)

206
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,630
(No.)

207
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,870
(I have to keep acting
lovey-dovey with Pan Yang.)

208
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,120
No.

209
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,240
We're not getting a divorce.

210
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:50,320
My husband and I were just bickering.

211
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,550
We were only speaking in anger.

212
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,440
Married couples argue all the time.

213
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:56,030
They always make up in the end.

214
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:57,440
Li Qingqing, have you no shame?

215
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,440
Pan Yang doesn't love you at all.

216
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,670
Yet you still throw yourself at him.

217
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,750
So what?

218
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,320
I don't care.

219
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,240
Even if

220
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,910
he marries another woman,

221
00:11:11,150 --> 00:11:13,510
would you still want
to grow old with him?

222
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:18,690
My husband has spent years
fighting on the battlefield.

223
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:21,910
Surely my husband remembers

224
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:25,320
all I've done to keep
this household running.

225
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:27,320
When you said you wanted to divorce me,

226
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,630
you were only speaking in anger.

227
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,120
Isn't that right, my dear?

228
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,030
Yes.

229
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,630
I was only speaking in anger.

230
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,270
(She's actually
willing to humble herself)

231
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,480
(for that fool?)

232
00:11:44,630 --> 00:11:46,670
Since General Pan and your wife

233
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:49,030
are so deeply devoted to each other,

234
00:11:50,870 --> 00:11:52,600
then consider my words unnecessary.

235
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:59,320
- Farewell, Your Highness.
- Farewell, Your Highness.

236
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,750
So why did the Crown Prince
come here in the first place?

237
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:08,820
(Thank goodness
that troublemaker is finally gone.)

238
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,510
(He scared me to death.)

239
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:13,720
(That wretched Li Qingqing.)

240
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:16,600
(She really is hopelessly
in love with me.)

241
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:19,320
Not bad.

242
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:20,870
You've got good taste.

243
00:12:21,350 --> 00:12:23,120
At least you know
you can't live without me.

244
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:26,200
But don't think those little tricks

245
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,840
will make me look at you twice.

246
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,750
Behave yourself.

247
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,550
Take good care of Muyan and me.

248
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:33,240
Stop causing trouble

249
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,480
for this family.

250
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,440
Keep running your mouth.

251
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,910
I'll beat you up.

252
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,150
I was just starting
to be nicer to you, and you...

253
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:39,670
Me...

254
00:12:41,150 --> 00:12:41,840
Yang!

255
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,320
How dare you kick me!

256
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,750
Qingqing.

257
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:46,510
How could you hit Yang?

258
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:47,120
What?

259
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,270
Jealous?

260
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,360
Want me to kick you too?

261
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:58,000
My dear, look at Qingqing.

262
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,960
She's becoming more and more outrageous.

263
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:01,240
Yesterday she slapped you.

264
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,630
Today she kicked you.

265
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,720
If you keep putting up with this,

266
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:06,570
she'll be completely
out of control sooner or later.

267
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,440
Don't you understand?

268
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:13,960
That wretched woman
has no intention of divorcing me.

269
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:17,240
Everything she's done
is just to get close to me

270
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,500
and keep me tangled up with her.

271
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:21,150
I won't give her the satisfaction.

272
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:22,840
Ignoring her

273
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:25,870
is the greatest punishment
I can give her.

274
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,720
Tell Pan Yang

275
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,720
he is to report to the Inspectorate

276
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,720
starting tomorrow.

277
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:50,060
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

278
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:54,200
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

279
00:13:54,970 --> 00:13:56,710
♪Your smile♪

280
00:13:56,970 --> 00:13:59,260
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

281
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:02,940
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

282
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:06,710
♪Yet I stand before you♪

283
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:11,280
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

284
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:13,620
♪Though fate tries♪

285
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:16,200
♪To make us pass each other by♪

286
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:19,840
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

287
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,730
♪Though time slips by♪

288
00:14:21,730 --> 00:14:23,490
♪As day turns into night♪

289
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:28,030
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

290
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:30,830
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

291
00:14:30,830 --> 00:14:32,620
♪Blessed by fate♪

292
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:37,780
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

293
00:14:37,780 --> 00:14:40,220
♪Your smiling face♪

294
00:14:40,220 --> 00:14:43,060
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

295
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:46,680
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

296
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:50,660
♪And wander the world together♪

297
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:52,000
♪Holding you close♪

298
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,540
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

299
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:56,860
♪Your tenderness♪

300
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:59,720
♪Is the brightest moon♪

301
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:03,420
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

302
00:15:03,940 --> 00:15:07,230
♪Our love will never fade away♪

303
00:15:07,230 --> 00:15:09,690
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

304
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:14,470
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

